OL,3,CLast Orders: Middle East conflict and
OL,4,Cparliament's proposed house move
OL,6,FITV Yorkshire's political programme
OL,7,FLast Orders returns with political
OL,8,Fcorrespondent Fred Dimbleby.
OL,10,FHe's joined by Ben Bradley, of Reform
OL,11,FUK, Natalie Fleet, the Labour MP for
OL,12,FBolsover, and Conservative Baroness
OL,13,FAnne McIntosh to discuss the domestic
OL,14,Feffects of the Middle East conflict
OL,15,Fand whether Parliament should relocate
OL,16,Fto allow for multi-billion pound
OL,17,Frepairs.
